data.description:
GATED COMMUNITY! Your dream home is here! Single-story gem providing 3 beds, 2 baths, and a 3 car garage. The delightful interior has a great open floor plan w/awesome back patio access and upgraded interior finishes. There is abundant natural light, neutral paint, gorgeous tile floors in the main areas, & carpet in bedrooms. Immaculate kitchen is equipped with quartz/marble counters, tile backsplash, an island w/breakfast bar, rich cabinetry, and SS appliances. Master bedroom boasts a lavish ensuite w/dual sinks, tub, separate shower & walk-in closet. The backyard is ready for entertaining with its covered patio, travertine tiles, and large turf area. Excellent lot located nearby the community playground!

Seller is licensed Real Estate Agent
